title: Wanna find people to play with - Dumbledour (Oceania)
body:
I used to play on EU West&East but moved to Nz and dont know anyone here, so kinda boring playing games by myself. Trying to lvl up a new account here instead of transfering, im lvl 24 at this moment and I used to play all lanes, but ive mainly played top and supp, but trying to learn all lanes better too! 

So anyone up for normals and later on ranked when i reach a higher lvl?

replies.body: Hey! Im keen to play with new people, add my smurf "GeneralDunk" we can lvl together cause leveling is kinda boring for me rn

Hai! Im keen to maybe us 3 could play? I'm a pretty low lvl right now and wanna level it up, ill send you a fq? My IGN is "Talón" and yea I'd like to join you guys if you are duoing cause it's a little boring playing by myself and all the people I play with are actually new or some Korean guys that don't know English
